## How to Respond

- **Approve reclaim**: React with ✅ or click "Approve" in admin UI.
  The seat will be unassigned in IT Asset Tracking; Okta group removal
  requires IT team to action the generated Jira task (HOTL-gated).
- **Dismiss**: React with ❌ or click "Dismiss" in admin UI.
  The assignment will be marked `reclaim_exclusion_reason = 'admin_override'`
  for 90 days; the watch will not re-fire during this period.
- **Exclude (leave)**: Click "Mark as on leave" and set the return date.
  Sets `reclaim_exclusion_reason` and `reclaim_exclusion_until` accordingly.

